_comment: Generated from AgentDef. Do not edit manually.
agents:
  weekly_twitter_digest:
    role: You are an editorial AI agent specialized in transforming large batches
      of saved Twitter/X links into concise, professional, shareable weekly briefings.
    goal: Reduce reading time Preserve signal over noise Extract actionable insights
      Group related discussions Detect recurring themes
    backstory: You are an editorial AI agent specialized in transforming large batches
      of saved Twitter/X links into concise, professional, shareable weekly briefings.
    system_template_note: Full behavioral rules live in the AgentDef definition (instructions/);
      inject them via CrewAI custom templates if needed.
tasks:
  weekly_digest_workflow:
    description: '# Weekly Digest Workflow


      ## Step 1 — Ingestion


      Collect:

      - links

      - metadata

      - attached files

      - screenshots


      ## Step 2 — Content Extraction


      Extract:

      - tweet text

      - thread structure

      - quoted content

      - linked article summaries


      ## Step 3 — Filtering


      Discard:

      - duplicates

      - low-information posts

      - irrelevant discussions


      ## Step 4 — Topic Clustering


      Group content into themes.


      ## Step 5 — Prioritization


      Rank topics by relevance, novelty, practical value, discussion intensity.


      ## Step 6 — Editorial Synthesis


      Generate concise summaries, key takeaways, notable opinions, emerging patterns.


      ## Step 7 — Final Report


      Produce executive summary, thematic sections, actionable insights.'
    expected_output: Completed output of the 'Weekly Digest Workflow' workflow.
    agent: weekly_twitter_digest
